00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:10,030
a few fights here,

582
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:11,390
so we've met before.

583
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:12,790
Ms. Zhou

584
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:14,880
