585
00:29:15,070 --> 00:29:15,440
Okay.

586
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:17,090
Hello, officer.

587
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,480
Hello, officer.

588
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:20,200
Hello, officer.

589
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:22,240
Hello, Wang.

590
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:25,890
Mind your manners.

591
00:29:26,270 --> 00:29:27,470
Hello, Officer Wang.

592
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:29,640
This is Chief Zhang.

593
00:29:30,110 --> 00:29:30,750
Hello.

594
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:31,590
We're here today

595
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:32,350
because there are some situations

596
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:33,510
we want to ask you about.

597
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:35,110
I'll definitely cooperate.

598
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:35,970
Have a seat.

599
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:41,300
[Zhou Qi,
Fenglinwan Hotel's PR Manager]

600
00:29:46,310 --> 00:29:46,790
Chief.

601
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:49,440
Chief.

602
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:54,090
What we're asking you

603
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,400
today

604
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,200
must be forgotten

605
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:58,130
or kept a secret.

606
00:29:58,480 --> 00:29:59,210
Understand?

607
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,840
I'll 100% keep it a secret.

608
00:30:02,310 --> 00:30:03,760
I understand the rules.

609
00:30:04,270 --> 00:30:05,650
Whatever you ask,

610
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,000
I'll answer honestly

611
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:08,410
and fulfill my duty.

612
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:09,750
Good, good.

613
00:30:15,350 --> 00:30:15,750
Chief,

614
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:16,640
go ahead.

615
00:30:24,270 --> 00:30:25,330
Do you know Ye Jian?

616
00:30:26,590 --> 00:30:27,450
Captain Ye?

617
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:28,200
Yes.

618
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,590
Has Captain Ye been

619
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:38,720
to Fenglinwan Hotel

620
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,320
or your nightclub recently?

621
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:47,690
Are you sure?

622
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:50,120
I didn't see him anyway.

623
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,240
Anything else?

624
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:17,590
If not,

625
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:19,720
officers, I'll head back first.

626
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:22,510
Wait.

627
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,550
If you think of

628
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,350
anything suspicious,

629
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:28,550
