630
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:29,520
Of course.

631
00:31:35,510 --> 00:31:36,240
Done asking?

632
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:38,110
Do you have anything to ask?

633
00:31:38,110 --> 00:31:39,240
N-No, I don't.

634
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:40,970
Neither do I.

635
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:42,960
She looks like

636
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:44,060
