637
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:49,570
I want to see Lu Yibo.

638
00:31:49,830 --> 00:31:50,510
Make an appointment for me—

639
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:51,110
right now.

640
00:32:02,070 --> 00:32:03,600
Can you still see anything?

641
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:08,000
Can you find him?

642
00:32:12,590 --> 00:32:12,990
Got it.

643
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:14,340
Can you hear me?

644
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:17,270
Can you hear me?

645
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:18,830
Found him.

646
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,860
Is it the guy in the garden?

647
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:24,230
Chief Huang.

648
00:32:24,470 --> 00:32:26,550
The signal at my house was bad just now.

649
00:32:26,550 --> 00:32:27,370
It's fine now.

650
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,770
Go ahead.

651
00:32:29,110 --> 00:32:29,880
Fang,

652
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:31,790
