653
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:34,830
It's time to step back
and take care of our health.

654
00:32:34,830 --> 00:32:36,890
Don't you like doing cultural stuff?

655
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,720
Switching to an easier job

656
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:40,750
would make you happy, right?

657
00:32:42,790 --> 00:32:43,560
How's that?

658
00:32:43,590 --> 00:32:44,720
Are you so happy that

659
00:32:44,830 --> 00:32:45,960
you can't speak?

660
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:47,140
Well...

661
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,400
Why?

662
00:32:49,110 --> 00:32:51,030
We mainly considered how

663
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:52,310
