664
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,550
and hardworking all these years—

665
00:32:53,550 --> 00:32:54,840
it hasn't been easy.

666
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,340
N-No, Chief Huang.

667
00:32:56,790 --> 00:32:58,850
I can really work for another 2 years.

668
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:01,550
I've been fighting for a chance for you.

669
00:33:01,550 --> 00:33:03,410
And I finally got it this time.

670
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:06,400
Why bother, Chief Huang?

671
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,730
What are you talking about?

672
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,880
You only have work in your heart.

673
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:13,120
So I can't not have you in mine.

674
00:33:13,830 --> 00:33:14,440
Fang,

675
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:16,620
wrap up your work nicely

676
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,510
and get ready
to go to the provincial capital

677
00:33:18,510 --> 00:33:20,170
to do your cultural research.

678
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:25,440
Fang?

679
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:28,110
Why aren't you laughing?

680
00:33:32,110 --> 00:33:33,160
All right, all right.

681
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:33,850
No need for

682
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:34,790
words of gratitude.

683
00:33:34,790 --> 00:33:35,620
That's it.

684
00:33:42,270 --> 00:33:43,460
What is he doing?

685
00:33:43,790 --> 00:33:45,790
Looks like Five-Animal Exercises.

686
00:33:45,790 --> 00:33:47,250
He cares about his health.

687
00:33:50,590 --> 00:33:51,030
Bro,

688
00:33:51,790 --> 00:33:52,630
let's go.

689
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:53,880
I'm hungry.

690
00:33:54,070 --> 00:33:55,930
Knowing where he lives is enough.

691
00:33:57,590 --> 00:33:58,200
We have to

692
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,600
keep watch here tonight.

693
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:00,720
That way, when he leaves tomorrow,

694
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:01,850
we can make our move.

695
00:34:06,550 --> 00:34:07,280
Makes sense.

696
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:14,000
Chief Zhang,

697
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:15,530
how should we ask him later?

698
00:34:17,190 --> 00:34:18,960
Do you like
listening to Guo Degang's crosstalk?

699
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:19,630
Yes.

700
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:20,190
Yes?

701
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:22,510
I heard that sometimes
when he's on stage with Yu Qian,

702
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:23,150
they don't

703
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:24,310
follow the script.

704
00:34:24,630 --> 00:34:25,440
Improvising?

705
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,239
Right.

706
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:27,230
All right then,

707
00:34:27,230 --> 00:34:28,000
as long as you deliver the setup,

708
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:28,800
I'll play along.

709
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:29,659
You sure? Okay.

710
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:33,670
Please.

711
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:34,130
Please.

712
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:39,429
What a luxurious office.

713
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:41,440
It's converted from a presidential suite.

714
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,360
Have a seat, officers.

715
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:42,760
Sit.

716
00:34:43,070 --> 00:34:43,510
Sit.

717
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:49,840
If you're standing, we...

718
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,480
Sit.

719
00:34:50,550 --> 00:34:51,320
I'll sit.

720
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:55,920
Officers,

721
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:57,570
what can I do for you?

722
00:34:58,110 --> 00:35:01,060
Well, we just saw each other recently

723
00:35:01,150 --> 00:35:02,360
at Captain Ye's memorial service,

724
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,320
didn't we?

725
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:05,800
Mr. Lu,

726
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,000
guess why we're here.

727
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:11,960
I don't know.

728
00:35:47,150 --> 00:35:48,350
I am a police officer!

729
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:48,960
Listen to me!

730
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,220
Don't run this way now.

731
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,070
You, get out of the way.

732
00:35:51,070 --> 00:35:52,030
Don't go that way!

733
00:35:52,030 --> 00:35:52,770
Move!

734
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,440
Go around! Go around!

735
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:06,840
Don't take it out.

736
00:36:10,030 --> 00:36:11,630
I've been prepared for this.

737
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:14,920
What's meant to come will come.

738
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:23,000
You can take it out and see for yourself.

739
00:36:32,750 --> 00:36:33,660
Chief Zhang,

740
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,000
a leader from the Provincial Department

741
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,400
assigned to this special case.

742
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,530
He came with clues,

743
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:39,940
so it's all down to your attitude now.

744
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:50,420
I wrote the report letter.

745
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:01,480
You wrote the report letter?

746
00:37:01,870 --> 00:37:02,680
I didn't write it?

747
00:37:02,680 --> 00:37:03,910
You did.

748
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:09,050
You aren't here for this?

749
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:11,110
That's exactly what we are here for.

750
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,440
This file...

751
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:14,090
Your report letter

752
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,540
