and writing over—it's illegible.

754
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,440
We have to verify it

755
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:19,550
with you in person.

756
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,020
Yes.

757
00:37:22,230 --> 00:37:23,270
I was really

758
00:37:24,230 --> 00:37:25,630
too agitated at the time.

759
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:28,130
Who killed Lu Zheng?

760
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,180
I don't know.

761
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,750
Then who did you report?

762
00:37:35,230 --> 00:37:37,160
You should at least remember that.

763
00:37:58,840 --> 00:38:00,370
The person I reported is...

764
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,230
Who was it again?

765
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:10,920
Let me tell you.

766
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,070
I'm giving you a chance right now

767
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:13,230
to make up for your crimes.

768
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,230
If we didn't know the actual situation,

769
00:38:14,230 --> 00:38:15,280
would we come looking for you?

770
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:17,880
If you don't want to talk,
we can talk at the station.

771
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,960
Mr. Lu is our witness now.

772
00:38:20,110 --> 00:38:22,110
He is the key
to helping us solve the case.

773
00:38:22,110 --> 00:38:23,360
We can't treat witnesses

774
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,760
like criminal suspects.

775
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:25,280
You...

776
00:38:31,630 --> 00:38:32,590
Tell us yourself.

777
00:38:32,590 --> 00:38:33,190
Who is it?

778
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:41,530
Chief Zhang.

779
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:46,460
I need to think about it again.

780
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:49,680
Can you give me some time?

781
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:52,760
Yes, absolutely.

782
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:54,480
We protect witnesses.
